    <div class="container">
      <h2>About TaftBites</h2>
      <p>A full-stack restaurant review web application for students and food lovers near <strong>De La Salle University of Manila</strong>. Discover, review, and share your favorite dining spots along Taft Avenue.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="section container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>Project Overview</h2>
    </div>
    <p><strong>TaftBites</strong> provides users the capability to view and also write reviews for restaurants near De La Salle University, allowing them to select the right places that provide cuisine with the equivalent price and quality. This project aims to replicate the system that pre-existing review sites such as Yelp, Tripadviser, and Google Maps, with a distinction of focusing for restaurants near De La Salle University Manila.
</p>
  </section>

  <section class="section-alt container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>Tech Stack & Dependencies</h2>
    </div>
    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Layer</th>
          <th>Technology / Package</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td>Frontend</td>
          <td>Handlebars, CSS, JavaScript</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Backend</td>
          <td>Node.js, Express.js</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Database</td>
          <td>MongoDB with Mongoose ODM</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Template Engine</td>
          <td>Express Handlebars</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <h3>Installed NPM Packages</h3>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>express</strong> — Web framework</li>
      <li><strong>express-handlebars</strong> — Template engine with layouts and partials</li>
      <li><strong>mongoose</strong> — MongoDB ODM</li>
      <li><strong>express-session</strong> — Session management for authentication</li>
      <li><strong>connect-mongo</strong> — Store sessions in MongoDB</li>
      <li><strong>dotenv</strong> — Load environment variables from .env</li>
      <li><strong>bcrypt</strong> — Password hashing</li>
      <li><strong>multer</strong> — File uploads (optional, for images)</li>
      <li><strong>cloudinary</strong> — Image hosting & transformations</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Third-Party Libraries</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Cloudinary API — Hosting images in the cloud</li>
      <li>MongoDB Compass — GUI for database management</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

